WEBVTT

00:00:50.155 --> 00:00:51.699
YTM NEWS LIVE BROADCAST

00:01:09.258 --> 00:01:11.385
I've been holding onto this case
for a long time,

00:01:12.261 --> 00:01:13.762
and I want to get to the bottom of it.

00:01:17.433 --> 00:01:18.684
Set up an interview for me.

00:01:19.184 --> 00:01:20.936
Make sure the interview
is on a reputable program

00:01:21.020 --> 00:01:23.606
that will give our story real credibility.

00:01:35.826 --> 00:01:36.785
Hi, I'm here.

00:01:36.869 --> 00:01:37.703
Yeah.

00:01:38.203 --> 00:01:41.332
Why are you here at this hour, though?
Did something happen?

00:01:41.415 --> 00:01:43.500
You said to call if I needed your help.

00:01:46.253 --> 00:01:47.087
What is it?

00:01:47.755 --> 00:01:49.048
What do you need my help with?

00:01:49.131 --> 00:01:50.090
Chairman Lee Dae-ho.

00:01:53.719 --> 00:01:54.803
Let's take him down.

00:01:57.264 --> 00:01:58.223
Together.

00:02:04.772 --> 00:02:06.315
YTM NEWS LIVE BROADCAST

00:02:06.398 --> 00:02:08.317
We'll wrap up the pre-interview here.

00:02:10.986 --> 00:02:13.489
It's my first time on live news,
so I'm really nervous.

00:02:14.365 --> 00:02:15.991
The anchor will make you feel at ease.

00:02:18.285 --> 00:02:19.286
By the way, ma'am.

00:02:20.537 --> 00:02:22.498
Can I ask you a favor?

00:02:23.082 --> 00:02:24.124
If we release this…

00:02:24.208 --> 00:02:27.461
Lim Hyeon-jun and Gwon Se-na
are the faces of the company.

00:02:27.544 --> 00:02:28.712
Won't they take a hit?

00:02:28.796 --> 00:02:30.506
I assume they have
shares in the company too.

00:02:30.589 --> 00:02:32.299
They won't be able to
avoid a hit entirely.

00:02:32.883 --> 00:02:36.178
But for now, I've taken
the best possible measures.

00:02:37.429 --> 00:02:38.305
Actually,

00:02:38.889 --> 00:02:40.557
I'm more concerned for Mr. Lee.

00:02:42.351 --> 00:02:43.686
Are you sure about this?

00:02:48.565 --> 00:02:50.192
It does weigh on me,

00:02:50.275 --> 00:02:52.736
but I've decided it's something I must do,

00:02:52.820 --> 00:02:55.572
so I'm willing to take any risk necessary.

00:02:56.323 --> 00:02:59.118
Then let's run this article as it is.

00:03:00.953 --> 00:03:03.080
Oh, also…

00:03:03.163 --> 00:03:05.499
I wanted to express my gratitude
to both of you.

00:03:07.209 --> 00:03:08.085
Thank you.

00:03:09.461 --> 00:03:11.005
YTM LIVE NEWS BROADCAST

00:03:45.706 --> 00:03:47.166
I went for a solemn look today.

00:03:48.834 --> 00:03:51.378
Well, this is my solemn look.

00:03:52.129 --> 00:03:52.963
Oh, yeah?

00:03:53.630 --> 00:03:54.798
I'm going to say

00:03:54.882 --> 00:03:56.717
some solemn things today.

00:03:58.635 --> 00:04:00.512
-Get ready for standby.
-Okay.

00:04:01.972 --> 00:04:02.890
Shall we go?

00:04:02.973 --> 00:04:05.309
You're watching our star interview
on YTM News.

00:04:05.392 --> 00:04:06.894
Lim Hyeon-jun and Gwon Se-na from

00:04:06.977 --> 00:04:09.563
Good Detective Kang Pil-gu
are here with us today.

00:04:09.646 --> 00:04:11.023
It's nice to meet you both.

00:04:11.106 --> 00:04:12.316
Yes, it's nice to meet you.

00:04:12.816 --> 00:04:14.401
I'm Lim Hyeon-jun,

00:04:14.485 --> 00:04:16.612
and I play Kang Pil-gu
in Good Detective Kang Pil-gu.

00:04:17.446 --> 00:04:18.655
Hello.

00:04:18.739 --> 00:04:21.158
I'm Gwon Se-na, and I play Seo I-su

00:04:21.241 --> 00:04:23.285
in season five
of Good Detective Kang Pil-gu.

00:04:23.869 --> 00:04:24.703
All right.

00:04:29.041 --> 00:04:29.875
It's ready to go.

00:04:36.507 --> 00:04:38.467
[EXCLUSIVE] THE UGLY TRUTH
BEHIND ENTERTAINMENT MOGUL LEE DAE-HO

00:04:38.842 --> 00:04:40.135
PUBLISH REQUEST SENT!

00:04:40.219 --> 00:04:43.472
The last question is for you, Mr. Lim.

00:04:43.555 --> 00:04:47.101
What do you think
Kang Pil-gu from season five

00:04:47.184 --> 00:04:49.269
has taught you?

00:04:50.187 --> 00:04:52.648
Kang Pil-gu always made the right choices

00:04:52.731 --> 00:04:54.316
and never regretted them.

00:04:55.150 --> 00:04:56.193
From now on,

00:04:56.276 --> 00:05:00.030
I want to live
just as sincerely and confidently.

00:05:01.698 --> 00:05:03.117
Ms. Gwon, I hear that you have

00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:06.495
something important to share
with our viewers today.

00:05:09.998 --> 00:05:10.999
Yes.

00:05:15.254 --> 00:05:16.130
The truth is--

00:05:16.213 --> 00:05:17.047
Wait.

00:05:18.382 --> 00:05:19.591
May I go first?

00:05:21.635 --> 00:05:22.594
Let's do that, then.

00:05:23.428 --> 00:05:27.182
A few months ago,
Ms. Gwon's agency merged with mine.

00:05:27.266 --> 00:05:30.227
Many people hoped
the integration would be beneficial,

00:05:30.310 --> 00:05:31.645
and I hoped the same.

00:05:31.728 --> 00:05:32.980
But I recently found out

00:05:33.063 --> 00:05:35.149
that Chairman Lee Dae-ho of Eunseong Group

00:05:35.649 --> 00:05:36.942
has been using our agency

00:05:37.442 --> 00:05:40.279
as a means to launder money.

00:05:40.779 --> 00:05:45.075
I apologize for raising an issue like this
during our drama promotion segment.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:47.327
But as a co-production partner
on Kang Pil-gu,

00:05:47.411 --> 00:05:49.037
I've invited a guest today

00:05:49.621 --> 00:05:51.999
to shed more light
on the details of this case.

00:06:18.734 --> 00:06:19.693
Hello.

00:06:20.819 --> 00:06:23.155
I'm Reporter Wi Jeong-sin
from Sports Eunseong.

00:06:24.698 --> 00:06:27.242
I'm here today

00:06:27.993 --> 00:06:31.246
to expose the ugly truth
behind the political and business circles.

00:06:31.330 --> 00:06:32.873
This case traces back seven years,

00:06:32.956 --> 00:06:36.376
to the death of an assemblyman's aide.

00:06:36.460 --> 00:06:37.961
Chairman Lee Dae-ho of Eunseong Group

00:06:38.045 --> 00:06:40.255
-put company funds in an illegal PE fund.
-Damn it!

00:06:40.339 --> 00:06:42.299
And in order to obtain information on
the Cheongwon City redevelopment project,

00:06:42.382 --> 00:06:44.301
he solicited favors from Ha Gee-wan,

00:06:44.384 --> 00:06:46.762
a former assemblyman
and the current FSS director.

00:06:47.596 --> 00:06:48.972
FINALE

00:06:59.691 --> 00:07:01.109
Everything will be okay.

00:07:01.902 --> 00:07:02.861
I'll see you on the set.

00:07:10.285 --> 00:07:12.537
You know, I came here today

00:07:12.621 --> 00:07:13.914
ready to expose everything.

00:07:16.625 --> 00:07:17.834
That's bold of you.

00:07:18.961 --> 00:07:20.003
Chairman Lee Dae-ho

00:07:21.171 --> 00:07:22.256
will stay out of sight for a while.

00:07:24.549 --> 00:07:26.426
Things will get quite messy for some time.

00:07:26.510 --> 00:07:27.761
I'm ready for it,

00:07:27.844 --> 00:07:29.388
so you should brace yourself.

00:07:32.557 --> 00:07:33.392
Well, both of you.

00:07:37.646 --> 00:07:38.522
Oh, by the way…

00:07:39.731 --> 00:07:40.691
Thank you.

00:08:03.088 --> 00:08:04.464
You did great.

00:08:06.883 --> 00:08:08.302
I'm kind of worried, though,

00:08:08.385 --> 00:08:10.304
now that your face has been exposed.

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:13.682
I know, right?

00:08:14.558 --> 00:08:17.185
Everyone saw my pretty face
on live national TV.

00:08:17.769 --> 00:08:18.645
I'm sure it caused a stir.

00:08:21.565 --> 00:08:22.983
What? I'm serious.

00:08:25.027 --> 00:08:26.987
I'm more worried about you, though.

00:08:27.571 --> 00:08:29.906
We did all that
while Kang Pil-gu is still on air.

00:08:31.408 --> 00:08:33.160
You're talking to Lim Hyeon-jun.

00:08:33.660 --> 00:08:36.663
I'm Kang Pil-gu, the symbol of justice.

00:08:44.129 --> 00:08:46.131
We did the right thing today.

00:08:47.674 --> 00:08:49.092
People will acknowledge it.

00:08:53.764 --> 00:08:54.598
Shall we go?

