-Do you feel any remorse?
-Anything to say to the public?

00:09:29.383 --> 00:09:31.259
Any comment
on the prosecution's investigation?

00:09:31.343 --> 00:09:33.637
Can we get a statement?

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.680
Do you have any comments on the slush fund

00:09:35.764 --> 00:09:37.599
tied to the Cheongwon City
redevelopment project?

00:09:43.146 --> 00:09:46.274
Lim Hyeon-jun helped this woman
expose Chairman Lee Dae-ho.

00:09:46.358 --> 00:09:49.069
During a Kang Pil-gu season five
promotion segment, no less.

00:09:49.152 --> 00:09:51.029
Now, why do you think
he helped this woman?

00:10:02.749 --> 00:10:06.253
Remember when Lim Hyeon-jun said
he liked someone at the press conference?

00:10:06.336 --> 00:10:07.879
Everyone was barking up the wrong tree

00:10:07.963 --> 00:10:09.714
when it was really Wi Jeong-sin all along.

00:10:09.798 --> 00:10:13.468
Does that mean she used her boyfriend
to take down Chairman Lee?

00:10:13.552 --> 00:10:15.178
Not just the chairman.

00:10:15.262 --> 00:10:17.931
Kang Pil-gu and Gwon Se-na
both took a hit.

00:10:18.014 --> 00:10:20.517
I heard Lim Hyeon-jun faces billions
in penalties for breaking ad contracts.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.769
Man, he's done for now.

00:10:23.311 --> 00:10:25.689
Wi Jeong-sin is the only one
who benefited from it all.

00:10:25.772 --> 00:10:26.815
She got an exclusive,

00:10:26.898 --> 00:10:28.817
made a name for herself,
and even has Mr. Lee in her corner.

00:10:28.900 --> 00:10:31.111
So none of you knew about this?

00:10:31.194 --> 00:10:32.154
Of course not.

00:10:32.237 --> 00:10:34.072
Wow, she's really something.

00:10:48.336 --> 00:10:49.379
Can you ring me up?

00:10:49.921 --> 00:10:50.755
Sure thing.

00:10:52.007 --> 00:10:53.300
Excuse me.

00:10:53.383 --> 00:10:54.968
Can I take that?

00:10:56.928 --> 00:10:58.430
Sure, go ahead.

00:11:14.154 --> 00:11:15.030
LIM HYEON-JUN, SIGNATURE

00:11:17.657 --> 00:11:18.909
-Here you go, sir.
-Thank you.

00:11:29.503 --> 00:11:32.631
You're Kang Pil-gu, right?

00:11:33.465 --> 00:11:35.175
Yes, that's me.

00:11:37.469 --> 00:11:41.389
Seeing how you're
putting the building up for a quick sale,

00:11:41.473 --> 00:11:43.016
I take it you need cash quickly.

00:11:44.976 --> 00:11:47.020
Yes, I guess so.

00:11:59.074 --> 00:12:00.575
Stop polishing it.

00:12:00.659 --> 00:12:03.245
The car's already sold,
so what are you shining it up for?

00:12:03.328 --> 00:12:07.541
Come on, if it looks nice and pretty,
the new owner will treat it better.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:09.334
This is so frustrating.

00:12:09.417 --> 00:12:11.753
Hey, enough with the sighing.

00:12:11.836 --> 00:12:13.255
It's my car I'm selling, not yours!

00:12:13.338 --> 00:12:14.965
And it's my building
I'm selling, not yours.

00:12:15.048 --> 00:12:18.260
Did Ms. Wi know things would get this bad
when she started all this?

00:12:18.343 --> 00:12:21.930
How many times do I have to tell you
I'm the one who asked her to go on TV?

00:12:22.013 --> 00:12:22.931
I'm glad you brought that up.

00:12:23.014 --> 00:12:24.808
You're not a reporter, she is.

00:12:24.891 --> 00:12:27.394
Thanks to that damn live broadcast,

00:12:27.477 --> 00:12:29.104
our company got raided,

00:12:29.187 --> 00:12:31.982
and you had to sell your building and car
to cover the ad contract penalties!

00:12:32.065 --> 00:12:34.776
And what about Kang Pil-gu now?

00:12:34.859 --> 00:12:39.281
Jeez, if people enjoy Kang Pil-gu,
the ratings will bounce back.

00:12:39.364 --> 00:12:43.034
And the ad deals will come back
once my public image is restored.

00:12:45.245 --> 00:12:48.498
It won't be long
before people find out the truth.

00:12:49.708 --> 00:12:51.084
I'm sure of it.

00:12:52.961 --> 00:12:56.256
Why couldn't you just wait until
the drama was over to release the article?

00:12:56.339 --> 00:12:57.632
Why do it while it's still airing?

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:00.343
The ratings are low as they are.

00:13:00.427 --> 00:13:02.137
Why couldn't you just promote it
like you were told?

00:13:02.220 --> 00:13:03.847
Hey, it did help promote the show.

00:13:03.930 --> 00:13:04.806
It caused a buzz, no?

00:13:04.889 --> 00:13:05.849
No.

00:13:06.474 --> 00:13:07.475
Oh, really?

00:13:10.979 --> 00:13:13.607
Why didn't you talk him out of it, Ms. Wi?

00:13:15.483 --> 00:13:18.528
I'm sorry. There's nothing I can say.

00:13:20.655 --> 00:13:21.740
How's…

00:13:22.574 --> 00:13:23.825
Mr. Lim doing?

00:13:23.908 --> 00:13:25.243
He's going through a lot.

00:13:25.869 --> 00:13:27.495
He's selling off his building and car

00:13:27.579 --> 00:13:29.080
and took out a mortgage on his home

00:13:29.581 --> 00:13:31.583
to pay the penalties
for breaking his ad contracts.

00:13:32.083 --> 00:13:34.294
Are the penalties that steep?

00:13:35.754 --> 00:13:37.005
With that being said,

00:13:37.088 --> 00:13:39.090
about the article you promised to release.

00:13:39.174 --> 00:13:40.842
Could you get it out as soon as possible?

00:13:43.178 --> 00:13:44.971
Article releases are all about timing.

00:13:46.097 --> 00:13:47.891
If we release it immediately,

00:13:47.974 --> 00:13:51.019
people will accuse Mr. Lim
of trying to avoid responsibility.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:54.981
I suggest we hold off and publish it
when things are at their worst.

00:13:55.649 --> 00:13:57.317
That way, public opinion
will turn dramatically.

00:13:57.400 --> 00:13:58.443
Will it, though?

00:13:58.526 --> 00:14:00.320
Money is one thing.

00:14:00.403 --> 00:14:02.989
But his public image as an actor
has taken too much of a hit,

00:14:03.073 --> 00:14:05.033
and he's no longer getting
any new project offers.

00:14:05.116 --> 00:14:06.117
At this rate,

00:14:06.201 --> 00:14:08.703
we might just end up
running a print shop again.

00:14:15.502 --> 00:14:17.212
He's selling off his building and car

00:14:17.295 --> 00:14:18.672
and took out a mortgage on his home

00:14:18.755 --> 00:14:20.382
to pay the penalties
for breaking his ad contracts.

00:14:40.110 --> 00:14:43.988
[EUNSEONGILBO] RECRUITMENT NOTICE:
SERIA TEMPORARY ASSIGNMENT

00:14:48.993 --> 00:14:51.037
How are you holding up, Ms. Wi?

00:14:51.871 --> 00:14:53.164
Yes, I'm fine.

00:14:53.248 --> 00:14:55.875
Everyone's asking to confirm
your relationship with Lim Hyeon-jun.

00:14:55.959 --> 00:14:59.045
In fact, why don't you let us
write about your dating rumor?

00:14:59.629 --> 00:15:00.672
I know I'll do a good job.

00:15:00.755 --> 00:15:01.881
Jeez.

00:15:01.965 --> 00:15:02.966
What?

00:15:06.469 --> 00:15:07.345
Mr. Lee.

00:15:08.304 --> 00:15:11.015
I saw the Seria
temporary assignment notice.

00:15:11.099 --> 00:15:12.142
Has the position been filled?

00:15:12.225 --> 00:15:15.270
No, I believe no one has applied yet.

00:15:15.353 --> 00:15:17.647
Then I'll go.

00:15:17.731 --> 00:15:19.232
-What?
-No, you can't do that.

00:15:19.315 --> 00:15:22.110
If you're worried about
going straight to the political desk--

00:15:22.193 --> 00:15:24.028
It has nothing to do with that.

00:15:24.612 --> 00:15:25.989
It's fine if I never go back.

00:15:26.072 --> 00:15:28.074
Then why do you insist on going
to that dangerous place?

00:15:31.286 --> 00:15:32.495
If I let things go on like this,

00:15:33.163 --> 00:15:36.499
everyone will assume all the rumors
about Mr. Lim are true.

00:15:37.083 --> 00:15:39.210
The dating rumor will break out
no matter what we do,

00:15:39.294 --> 00:15:42.589
and Chairman Lee Dae-ho's case
will get overshadowed and ignored.

00:15:42.672 --> 00:15:44.674
It may never fully come to light.

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:48.386
You both know that the media
is already trying to spin this.

00:15:48.470 --> 00:15:50.680
Even so, you going to Seria

00:15:50.764 --> 00:15:52.766
won't resolve anything.

00:15:52.849 --> 00:15:53.683
You're right.

00:15:54.768 --> 00:15:57.479
But it'll at least shut down
the dating rumor.

00:15:57.979 --> 00:15:58.980
That way,

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:01.858
things will settle faster.

00:16:28.510 --> 00:16:29.677
REPORTER WI JEONG-SIN

00:16:34.265 --> 00:16:36.184
Why is it so hard to get hold of you?

00:16:36.726 --> 00:16:37.560
Is something wrong?

00:16:38.436 --> 00:16:40.522
You have it worse than I do, Mr. Lim.

00:16:42.315 --> 00:16:44.108
I heard filming has resumed.

00:16:44.818 --> 00:16:45.985
Aren't you busy?

00:16:46.069 --> 00:16:48.154
Exactly. I'm the one who's busy,

00:16:48.238 --> 00:16:50.907
so why is it so hard to reach you?

00:16:50.990 --> 00:16:51.866
I'm sorry.

00:16:52.742 --> 00:16:54.202
Do you have some time?

00:16:55.203 --> 00:16:56.412
Of course, I do!

00:16:56.496 --> 00:16:59.541
-Jeez, where are we going?
-Just come. Hurry up.

00:16:59.624 --> 00:17:01.668
It's right here.

00:17:01.751 --> 00:17:03.711
-We're here.
-A video arcade?

00:17:06.881 --> 00:17:08.591
Look, it's Kang Pil-gu!

00:17:08.675 --> 00:17:10.635
You have to lower the claw
around the body.

00:17:10.718 --> 00:17:13.137
-Come on.
-Have you never done this before?

00:17:16.474 --> 00:17:18.643
-Darn it!
-Come on.

00:17:18.726 --> 00:17:21.563
-It's all about accuracy. Try again.
-Okay.

00:17:21.646 --> 00:17:23.731
Yes, right there. Just a bit more…

00:17:24.399 --> 00:17:27.193
-No, I got it!
-You have to aim higher!

00:17:27.277 --> 00:17:29.487
Just trust me. Right now!

00:17:32.448 --> 00:17:33.283
Oh, come on!

00:17:34.868 --> 00:17:36.035
Seriously?

00:17:36.119 --> 00:17:37.829
Don't do that.

00:17:38.413 --> 00:17:40.540
Jeez, this is how you do it.

00:17:48.172 --> 00:17:49.132
Yes!

00:18:02.520 --> 00:18:03.980
Why is this place so empty?

00:18:04.063 --> 00:18:05.315
I rented out the whole place.

00:18:06.190 --> 00:18:07.275
What?

00:18:07.984 --> 00:18:10.320
I can't rent out a place for free
like you can,

00:18:10.987 --> 00:18:13.072
but adults are at work,
and students are at school

00:18:13.573 --> 00:18:14.490
on a weekday like this.

00:18:15.450 --> 00:18:16.576
So I rented it at a low price.

00:18:17.285 --> 00:18:19.412
Why did you spend money on this?

