There.

00:18:42.727 --> 00:18:43.645
Smile!

00:18:46.356 --> 00:18:47.315
Try these on too.

00:18:52.654 --> 00:18:53.696
Smile!

00:18:56.741 --> 00:18:57.575
Smile!

