Man, it's been ages since I've had
ramyeon at a convenience store.

00:19:23.893 --> 00:19:24.852
So I guess you're fine with this.

00:19:25.603 --> 00:19:28.272
You grumbled so much
when we had ramyeon at the Hangang River.

00:19:29.565 --> 00:19:32.610
Only teenagers come here to eat ramyeon

00:19:32.694 --> 00:19:34.028
and make memories over it.

00:19:34.612 --> 00:19:36.406
I can't believe I'm doing this at my age.

00:19:37.031 --> 00:19:39.242
I tend to grumble even if I'm happy.

00:19:39.784 --> 00:19:41.869
I really enjoyed that day, you know.

00:19:54.465 --> 00:19:55.299
What about today?

00:19:56.050 --> 00:19:56.968
Did you enjoy it too?

00:19:57.927 --> 00:20:00.680
You said what you envied the most
was an ordinary life.

00:20:01.347 --> 00:20:04.475
That's why I wanted to
spend an ordinary day with you,

00:20:04.559 --> 00:20:05.852
just like everyone else.

00:20:07.228 --> 00:20:08.396
So how was it? Did you enjoy it?

00:20:08.479 --> 00:20:09.981
It couldn't have been better.

00:20:10.481 --> 00:20:11.315
It was a date, after all.

00:20:15.236 --> 00:20:16.070
The truth is…

00:20:17.447 --> 00:20:18.948
there's something I need to tell you.

00:20:20.908 --> 00:20:22.076
Seria?

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:23.661
You're going to a war zone?

00:20:23.745 --> 00:20:24.871
Are you insane?

00:20:24.954 --> 00:20:27.582
I know it's dangerous,
but I've been there before--

00:20:27.665 --> 00:20:29.542
Exactly, you've been there already!

00:20:29.625 --> 00:20:31.002
So why go back to a war zone?

00:20:31.085 --> 00:20:32.420
To return to the political desk.

00:20:35.673 --> 00:20:36.507
Also,

00:20:36.591 --> 00:20:39.927
did you even consider me
when you made that decision?

00:20:40.762 --> 00:20:43.890
Is that why
you took me to the arcade today?

00:20:43.973 --> 00:20:45.266
Are you some cruel mom

00:20:45.349 --> 00:20:47.894
who takes her kid to the park
before abandoning him?

00:20:47.977 --> 00:20:50.563
How could you do this
without talking to me first?

00:20:50.646 --> 00:20:52.190
A cruel mom who abandons her kid?

00:20:52.273 --> 00:20:53.858
How could you say that to me?

00:20:53.941 --> 00:20:55.693
I wanted us to have a good time,

00:20:55.777 --> 00:20:58.029
so I spent all day thinking about
how to make it enjoyable for us.

00:20:58.988 --> 00:21:01.032
Why would you dismiss the effort I put in?

00:21:01.115 --> 00:21:03.534
Why are you getting angry at me?

00:21:03.618 --> 00:21:04.535
So you think

00:21:04.619 --> 00:21:06.537
pulling a stunt
like going to Seria was smart?

00:21:06.621 --> 00:21:07.580
"Pulling a stunt"?

00:21:07.663 --> 00:21:09.040
Of course, it's a stunt!

00:21:09.123 --> 00:21:11.417
Are you showing off
or just being reckless?

00:21:11.501 --> 00:21:13.753
How does it make any sense for you to say

00:21:13.836 --> 00:21:15.797
that you're going back there again?

00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:18.800
Do I look like someone
who would go there just to show off?

00:21:19.842 --> 00:21:21.844
I'm going there to work, not to have fun!

00:21:22.804 --> 00:21:23.721
I don't get it.

00:21:24.972 --> 00:21:26.641
Why are you doing this?

00:21:27.141 --> 00:21:28.810
You don't have to go!

00:21:29.727 --> 00:21:30.770
But I do.

00:21:33.898 --> 00:21:35.149
It's already been decided.

00:21:40.571 --> 00:21:41.572
Come on!

00:21:42.865 --> 00:21:43.866
Damn it!

00:21:47.203 --> 00:21:48.329
But why…

00:21:49.372 --> 00:21:50.456
You don't have to go.

00:21:51.332 --> 00:21:52.208
I mean…

00:22:04.512 --> 00:22:06.013
Seriously!

00:22:06.556 --> 00:22:07.640
Go.

00:22:07.723 --> 00:22:10.059
Just go! Leave!

00:22:13.437 --> 00:22:15.857
Don't you ever call me again!

00:22:15.940 --> 00:22:16.774
If you do, I'll…

00:22:28.077 --> 00:22:30.663
CHAIRMAN LEE DAE-HO ARRESTED ON CHARGES OF
MONEY LAUNDERING, SOLICITING MURDER…

00:22:51.642 --> 00:22:53.269
GWON SE-NA

00:22:53.352 --> 00:22:56.397
WOO YOUNG-SUK, AIDE

00:22:56.480 --> 00:22:58.524
CHAIRMAN LEE DAE-HO

00:23:35.561 --> 00:23:37.688
LIM HYEON-JUN

00:24:03.464 --> 00:24:04.757
You don't have to go!

00:24:05.341 --> 00:24:06.259
But I do.

00:24:08.678 --> 00:24:10.304
It's already been decided.

00:24:59.395 --> 00:25:00.354
Ms. Wi Jeong-sin?

00:25:01.355 --> 00:25:03.733
May I have a moment of your time?

00:25:17.204 --> 00:25:18.914
It's the first time in my life.

00:25:18.998 --> 00:25:20.541
I've never liked someone…

00:25:21.917 --> 00:25:23.586
so unconditionally.

00:25:45.524 --> 00:25:46.400
I like you.

00:25:49.153 --> 00:25:52.615
I haven't liked anyone
for a very long time.

00:25:55.034 --> 00:25:56.035
But…

00:25:57.787 --> 00:25:59.372
I have a feeling I'll like you…

00:26:01.415 --> 00:26:03.125
for a long time to come.

00:26:07.505 --> 00:26:08.422
Are you okay?

00:26:14.887 --> 00:26:17.765
Did you even consider me
when you made that decision?

00:26:18.516 --> 00:26:19.558
Are you some cruel mom

00:26:19.642 --> 00:26:21.769
who takes her kid to the park
before abandoning them!

00:26:21.852 --> 00:26:24.772
How could you do this
without talking to me first?

00:26:29.443 --> 00:26:30.611
So how was it? Did you enjoy it?

00:26:30.694 --> 00:26:32.238
It couldn't have been better.

00:26:32.780 --> 00:26:33.864
It was a date, after all.

00:26:38.202 --> 00:26:40.287
Even so, you going to Seria

00:26:40.371 --> 00:26:42.164
won't resolve anything.

00:26:44.875 --> 00:26:46.127
If I let things go on like this,

00:26:47.169 --> 00:26:50.506
everyone will assume all the rumors
about Mr. Lim are true.

00:27:09.984 --> 00:27:11.944
LIM HYEON-JUN

00:27:35.551 --> 00:27:37.052
If you go, when will you be back?

00:27:37.761 --> 00:27:39.305
I don't know for sure yet.

00:27:41.348 --> 00:27:43.100
How can you not know that?

00:27:43.184 --> 00:27:44.643
Then what am I supposed to do?

00:27:51.817 --> 00:27:53.694
Don't you hate me?

00:27:54.570 --> 00:27:56.030
You lost all your ad deals,

00:27:56.947 --> 00:27:58.282
and even your reputation hit rock bottom.

00:27:58.365 --> 00:28:00.910
I was the one who suggested it.
Why do you keep talking like it's on you?

00:28:04.455 --> 00:28:06.415
You can't possibly be okay.

00:28:08.292 --> 00:28:10.085
On top of all those articles
attacking you personally…

00:28:12.338 --> 00:28:14.048
even Kang Pil-gu is getting criticized.

00:28:15.007 --> 00:28:16.050
I don't regret what I did.

00:28:22.431 --> 00:28:23.849
I'm sorry about earlier.

00:28:25.142 --> 00:28:26.018
For getting mad at you.

00:28:27.436 --> 00:28:28.979
I was the one who raised my voice first.

00:28:30.898 --> 00:28:31.732
I'm sorry.

00:28:36.487 --> 00:28:38.072
So you're not mad at me anymore?

00:28:39.573 --> 00:28:41.158
I was never mad at you.

00:28:46.622 --> 00:28:47.456
I'll wait for you.

00:28:51.210 --> 00:28:52.753
-Mr. Lim--
-No.

00:28:53.671 --> 00:28:55.422
Waiting for you is my choice.

00:28:55.506 --> 00:28:57.258
You made your own choice to leave too.

00:29:00.553 --> 00:29:02.388
You're leaving the day after tomorrow?

00:29:03.055 --> 00:29:04.265
Yes.

00:29:05.599 --> 00:29:08.435
That's the last day of shooting
for Kang Pil-gu, right?

00:29:13.983 --> 00:29:14.984
Then today's our last day.

00:29:17.486 --> 00:29:19.363
Why would you say that?

00:29:19.446 --> 00:29:20.906
Like we'll never see each other again?

00:29:31.292 --> 00:29:32.751
Take care while I'm gone, okay?

00:30:00.904 --> 00:30:03.532
What if I begged you not to go?

00:30:06.493 --> 00:30:07.411
Would you still leave?

00:30:10.831 --> 00:30:11.874
Yes.

00:30:39.943 --> 00:30:41.570
Move that over there.

00:30:51.997 --> 00:30:54.500
LIM HYEON-JUN & WI JEONG-SIN

00:31:00.339 --> 00:31:02.091
Hey, can you bring that over?

00:31:03.592 --> 00:31:05.177
-Hey.
-Where does this go?

00:31:05.260 --> 00:31:06.095
Bro.

00:31:07.137 --> 00:31:08.055
It's time to finish up your makeup.

00:31:08.555 --> 00:31:09.390
Okay.

00:31:10.391 --> 00:31:11.266
Jeez.

00:31:11.975 --> 00:31:13.977
Ms. Wi must be on her way
to the airport by now.

00:31:15.312 --> 00:31:16.188
Let's go.

00:31:22.194 --> 00:31:23.737
I said I'd come with you.

00:31:23.821 --> 00:31:25.572
Forget it. Give me that.

00:31:29.785 --> 00:31:30.869
Take care of yourself.

00:31:30.953 --> 00:31:33.622
If you get hurt like last time,
I won't make it.

00:31:33.706 --> 00:31:34.748
Okay, I heard you.

00:31:45.050 --> 00:31:46.176
-Hello.
-Hello.

00:31:46.260 --> 00:31:48.804
Mr. Lim couldn't come,
so he asked me to take you to the airport.

00:31:48.887 --> 00:31:50.431
No, that's okay.

00:31:50.514 --> 00:31:52.099
Ms. Wi, if you don't get in,

00:31:52.182 --> 00:31:53.016
I'll get fired.

00:32:01.316 --> 00:32:02.484
I'll get in, then.

00:32:02.568 --> 00:32:03.444
Thank you.

00:33:21.230 --> 00:33:23.649
What am I going to do?

00:33:25.150 --> 00:33:26.318
Cut. Okay!

00:33:36.829 --> 00:33:37.913
Mr. Lim, that was great.

00:33:39.373 --> 00:33:40.207
Huh?

00:33:42.334 --> 00:33:43.335
Here.

00:33:43.877 --> 00:33:47.005
All right, that's a wrap
for Good Detective Kang Pil-gu Season 5.

00:33:47.089 --> 00:33:48.423
Thank you for all your hard work.

00:33:48.507 --> 00:33:49.633
Thank you!

00:33:55.722 --> 00:33:56.723
-Mr. Lim.
-Yeah?

00:33:57.432 --> 00:33:58.892
Thank you for all your hard work.

00:34:00.894 --> 00:34:02.312
I'm sorry for giving you a hard time.

00:34:02.980 --> 00:34:03.981
I mean it.

00:34:04.606 --> 00:34:06.358
Come on, Mr. Lim. Stop that.

00:34:07.484 --> 00:34:08.360
Byeong-gi…

00:34:10.237 --> 00:34:13.073
Mr. Lim, your acting today was phenomenal.

00:34:14.741 --> 00:34:15.576
Thank you.

00:34:16.368 --> 00:34:17.661
-Great work.
-You too.

00:34:30.757 --> 00:34:31.592
Bro!

00:34:32.426 --> 00:34:33.260
Look.

00:34:34.261 --> 00:34:35.137
Look at this.

00:34:36.013 --> 00:34:37.723
LIM HYEON-JUN & GWON SE-NA
ALREADY CUT TIES WITH CHAIRMAN LEE DAE-HO

00:34:38.557 --> 00:34:42.019
-Oh, it's been published.
-Ms. Wi really is something.

00:34:42.102 --> 00:34:44.021
She'd been thinking a step ahead

00:34:44.104 --> 00:34:47.024
to make a move
and turn the situation around.

00:34:47.774 --> 00:34:50.527
The advertisers have been
calling nonstop to apologize.

00:34:51.528 --> 00:34:53.447
When Ms. Wi said
we should donate our shares,

00:34:53.530 --> 00:34:55.157
what was your response again?

00:34:55.949 --> 00:34:58.035
Once Chairman Lee Dae-ho is exposed,

00:34:58.118 --> 00:34:59.828
it could cause a big problem
for the company

00:34:59.912 --> 00:35:01.330
and for both of you as well.

00:35:01.997 --> 00:35:03.081
So I was thinking…

00:35:04.207 --> 00:35:05.375
How about we do this?

00:35:05.459 --> 00:35:06.376
Do what?

00:35:06.460 --> 00:35:08.962
The two of you will take
all of your company shares

00:35:09.838 --> 00:35:11.340
-and donate them.
-Sure.

00:35:12.090 --> 00:35:13.383
-What?
-Let's do it.

00:35:13.884 --> 00:35:15.302
Come on, let's do it.

00:35:15.385 --> 00:35:18.305
You want us to donate our shares?

00:35:18.388 --> 00:35:20.223
-Like, all of it?
-Yes.

00:35:20.307 --> 00:35:21.725
Where should we donate it?

00:35:21.808 --> 00:35:24.394
What do you mean,
"Where should we donate it?"

00:35:24.478 --> 00:35:25.812
I can't do that!

00:35:26.396 --> 00:35:27.814
Come on.

00:35:27.898 --> 00:35:30.359
I donated it all anyway.

00:35:30.943 --> 00:35:33.487
Anyway, Ms. Wi saved us both.

00:35:33.570 --> 00:35:34.655
Right?

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.198
But I wonder why

00:35:36.281 --> 00:35:38.116
she released the article
under Ms. Yun's name.

00:35:38.200 --> 00:35:39.451
Because it'd look too set up?

00:35:44.081 --> 00:35:46.959
How could we possibly read into
Ms. Wi's master plan?

00:35:50.087 --> 00:35:52.255
By the way, I looked into that thing.

00:35:52.339 --> 00:35:55.092
There was an issue with
how your dismissal as CEO was handled.

00:35:55.175 --> 00:35:56.677
So you can actually be reinstated.

00:35:56.760 --> 00:35:58.261
-Seriously?
-Quiet.

00:35:58.345 --> 00:35:59.763
Hey, keep it down.

00:35:59.846 --> 00:36:02.140
-Seriously?
-Yes, but…

00:36:02.224 --> 00:36:04.893
Since you don't own a single share
of company stock,

00:36:04.977 --> 00:36:06.645
you could get fired at any time.

00:36:06.728 --> 00:36:09.815
So do a good job, okay?

00:36:09.898 --> 00:36:10.816
Got it?

00:36:12.067 --> 00:36:12.901
Okay.

